    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered here is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains factory-stiff with documented subframe reinforcement and a pristine M Variable differential. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the bushings, has been maintained to exacting standards. Finished in its original factory paint with zero oxidation, the exterior matches a cabin devoid of typical bolster wear or dash delamination. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
