    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true 'time capsule' specimen, meticulously preserved to meet the highest standards of a discerning collector. The exterior retains its original factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine and smoke-free, featuring premium leather upholstery with zero bolster wear and factory floor mats that have never seen a muddy boot. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the heated seats, functions as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is peerless, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and maintained strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule. I have a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt since the original delivery. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of corrosion or road salt. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality vehicle that looks, smells, and drives like new.",
