    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a speed-sensitive variable M-Differential Lock. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical audit, including a documented rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement for long-term chassis and internal engine integrity. The suspension maintains its factory geometry with crisp damping and no bushing deflection. Finished in pristine original paint with a flawless interior, this M3 represents a turn-key investment for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection and high-revving performance.",
